th Campus Plaza:SCP;Speech, Language, and Hearing Sciences:SLHS;Storm Hall West:SHW;Storm Hall:SH;Student Affairs (Imperial Valley):STAT;Student Center (Imperial Valley):STCT;Student Services East:SSE;Student Services West:SSW;Tenochca Hall:TENO;University Towers:UT;Villa Alvarado Apartments:VAA;West Commons:WC;Women's Resource Center:WRCT;Zura Hall:ZURA;"
